ygData.messageBody:
Hello, I am putting together a list that will soon be ready for all the
wizards of all of Norrath on any server(i.e. its not server specified,
just wizards, but we will soon be branching off into other classes!)!
This information is going to be VERY detailed, so me and Albryno would
really like it if anyone here is over lvl 29! We need a list of those
spells, what they do, actually, we need any information you got on
spells over lvl 29!
Thx for all the help :)
-Faldyin
